OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Ffine and dry this evening with some
OL,7,Flate sunshine. Cloud likely to
OL,8,Fincrease overnight, with some mist and
OL,9,Ffog in places, but remaining dry
OL,10,Facross the region.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FStaying largely dry again
OL,13,Fon Wednesday with a mix of cloud and
OL,14,Fspells of sunshine. An isolated shower
OL,15,Fcan't be ruled out but most places
OL,16,Favoiding them. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
