OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FThe
OL,6,Flargely dry, warm and settled theme
OL,7,Fcontinuing on Thursday and Friday. A
OL,8,Fchange in the weather then expected on
OL,9,FSaturday with some rain coming in.
